mailscraper

A simple cli utility for extracting email addresses from websites

USAGE:
  mailscraper [-v] [-t timeout] [-a useragent] url ...

FLAGS:
  -v           verbose logging to stderr
  -t duration  network timeout (e.g., 5s, 30s). default: 15s
  -a string    custom user agent

INSTALL:
  go build -o mailscraper .
